      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "\"I built an agent, now I need to\nwrite 200 lines of glue code just\nto connect it to yours, and if we\nswap in a third agent we start\nover from scratch.\"",
