      "text": "\"I built an agent. It follows the\nDarkMatter contract. Anyone can\ninstall it, run it, chain it with\nother agents, or swap it out.\nZero glue code.\"",
      "fontSize": 15,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "\"I built an agent. It follows the\nDarkMatter contract. Anyone can\ninstall it, run it, chain it with\nother agents, or swap it out.\nZero glue code.\"",
