      "updated": 1774803387277,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Then USB came along and said: \"Everyone use THIS one shape.\"\nNow any cable works with any device. One standard, everything connects.",
      "fontSize": 17,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Then USB came along and said: \"Everyone use THIS one shape.\"\nNow any cable works with any device. One standard, everything connects.",
