      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "It says: \"I don't care what kitchen you used to build your agent.\nAs long as you follow these 3 simple rules, your agent works everywhere.\"",
